# Force a single physical drizzle-orm install regardless of which peer
# set (kysely-or-not) consumers carry. Without this, better-auth pulls
# kysely as a runtime dep, which makes pnpm fork drizzle-orm into a
# kysely-peered copy distinct from the one @monmap/db uses — TypeScript
# then sees two unrelated `SQL<unknown>` types and the workspace fails
# to typecheck.
public-hoist-pattern[]=drizzle-orm
